---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout>
    <main class="container">
        <div class="about">
            <h1>About</h1>

            <div class="about-body">
                <p>Hi, I'm Colin Veron, a technical artist and computer science engineering student based in France.</p>

                <p>
                    My focus is shaders: real-time rendering, procedural visuals, the kind of work that lives at the
                    boundary between code and image. I'm still actively learning, and I want to keep going deeper into
                    every part of the technical artist role, tools, pipelines, rigging, whatever's next.
                </p>

                <p>
                    On this site you'll find personal projects like shader experiments, game development, 3D modeling,
                    and occasionally things that are harder to categorize. I also write technical articles. Most of what
                    I know I picked up from people who generously put their work out there on the internet. Writing here
                    is my way of giving back.
                </p>

                <p>
                    Outside of that I like piano (though I haven't touched it in months), learning languages, cooking
                    food (veggie here), and cats. I have one, very cute and very black.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="social-links">
